WEBVTT

00:01.658 --> 00:02.043
Hello.

00:02.231 --> 00:03.687
Thank you for calling Grand Hotel.

00:03.857 --> 00:04.753
My name is Laurie.

00:05.059 --> 00:06.055
How can I help you?

00:06.760 --> 00:07.187
Hello.

00:07.709 --> 00:12.783
A couple of weeks ago, I made a reservation and I have to cancel my reservation.

00:13.467 --> 00:14.337
Absolutely.

00:14.411 --> 00:16.741
Let me bring you up on the system here.

00:17.529 --> 00:19.357
Do you have the reservation number?

00:19.973 --> 00:21.193
Reservation number?

00:21.683 --> 00:25.147
Yeah, you received that when you called the first time.

00:26.516 --> 00:27.709
No, I haven't.

00:27.845 --> 00:29.475
I haven't received any.

00:30.158 --> 00:31.875
Oh, that's not a problem.

00:31.964 --> 00:33.717
I can look you up on the system.

00:34.021 --> 00:35.832
What's the last name on the reservation?

00:36.152 --> 00:36.510
Yes!

00:36.866 --> 00:38.773
My last name is Veltman.

00:38.994 --> 00:42.161
V E L T M A N.

00:42.964 --> 00:44.893
And what's your arrival date?

00:45.602 --> 00:46.833
October 12th.

00:47.297 --> 00:49.379
Okay, let me see here.

00:49.871 --> 00:50.657
Here you are!

00:51.013 --> 00:53.271
And you'd like me to cancel that reservation?

00:53.651 --> 00:55.690
I need to cancel the reservation, yes.

00:55.881 --> 00:57.399
No problem at all, sir.

00:57.529 --> 01:01.440
I just need the credit card number that you used to make the reservation with.

01:01.703 --> 01:02.376
Okay.

01:02.805 --> 01:08.916
My credit card number is 12345678900.

01:09.348 --> 01:13.789
Okay, I can cancel your reservation right now.

01:14.050 --> 01:14.770
Thanks.

